headline: What Analysts Think Is Changing The Story For loanDepot Now
summary: loanDepot’s latest price target revision has drawn fresh attention to how investors are recalibrating expectations around the lender’s future. While the fair value estimate and core assumptions like discount rate and revenue growth remain largely intact, the higher target reflects a delicate balance between optimism on execution and lingering doubts about long term momentum. Read on to see how you can track these shifting expectations over time and stay ahead of the evolving...
